---
title: Lentil, Vegetable & Butter Bean Chilli with Guacamole & Herby Rice
description: This chilli is a firm favourite of our chef Mimi. It is inspired by Mimi’s veggie friend Emily who whipped this up one night and having originally turned her nose up at lentils, Mimi proceeded to devour three portions. It is packed with a whole array of delicious ingredients and we hope you enjoy this taste sensation as much as we do!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55d34f2a79a23caa5f8b4567.jpg
